1
00:00:00,100 --> 00:00:02,900
Episode 51

2
00:00:03,594 --> 00:00:05,872
What a clever woman

3
00:00:07,200 --> 00:00:11,000
Do you know what I do

4
00:00:12,038 --> 00:00:13,053
to clever women?

5
00:00:14,601 --> 00:00:15,478
Kill me?

6
00:00:16,500 --> 00:00:19,627
but people who were saved do not kill their savior

7
00:00:21,941 --> 00:00:24,011
I never thought of killing you

8
00:00:25,300 --> 00:00:29,500
Smart women who are also beautiful

9
00:00:31,353 --> 00:00:34,677
It's very easy for people to like them

10
00:00:34,727 --> 00:00:35,569
This brother here

11
00:00:36,162 --> 00:00:38,242
Your comment is a little out of bound

12
00:00:40,300 --> 00:00:44,800
When we like something, we like them

13
00:00:46,084 --> 00:00:47,910
Not only like them

14
00:00:48,800 --> 00:00:51,700
We want to own them

15
00:00:59,039 --> 00:00:59,918
Don't forget

16
00:01:00,500 --> 00:01:03,000
this is my country

17
00:01:12,482 --> 00:01:12,601
There

18
00:01:12,601 --> 00:01:17,601
will be a day, that it can be ours as well ours

19
00:01:21,321 --> 00:01:22,973
We just saved your life

20
00:01:23,700 --> 00:01:25,900
We can also kill you

21
00:01:27,103 --> 00:01:28,804
With your ability?

22
00:01:29,917 --> 00:01:31,288
It won't be that easy

23
00:01:33,000 --> 00:01:36,000
Your Great Qing had a general named Nian Geng Yao in the past

24
00:01:37,123 --> 00:01:41,894
but recently you don't even have anyone near his ability

25
00:01:43,899 --> 00:01:46,346
not one that is comparable

26
00:01:47,826 --> 00:01:49,776
I won't even bat an eye

27
00:01:50,312 --> 00:01:51,866
but you're lucky

28
00:01:53,500 --> 00:01:54,900
because you're hurt

29
00:02:00,875 --> 00:02:01,695
Sir!

30
00:02:02,751 --> 00:02:03,951
Sir!

31
00:02:04,914 --> 00:02:06,321
Sir!

32
00:02:07,846 --> 00:02:10,571
You made us search for you so hard

33
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:12,300
What happened?

34
00:02:12,912 --> 00:02:17,123
Just now, i was bitten by a snake

35
00:02:18,500 --> 00:02:20,700
Luckily they saved me

36
00:02:25,290 --> 00:02:28,114
Thank you sir and miss

37
00:02:28,267 --> 00:02:29,590
for saving our master

38
00:02:30,063 --> 00:02:32,231
This master better becareful the next time he goes out

39
00:02:32,914 --> 00:02:36,835
Maybe next time, you won't be so carefree like today

40
00:02:38,200 --> 00:02:40,000
I understand the meaning of your words

41
00:02:40,700 --> 00:02:44,900
Of course as I can see that you're someone who values your life

42
00:02:46,300 --> 00:02:47,959
Judging from what you say

43
00:02:49,620 --> 00:02:51,522
you know half about me already

44
00:02:52,700 --> 00:02:54,488
You think that I know half about you

45
00:02:54,488 --> 00:02:58,100
but it will be my fortune not to ever bump into you again

46
00:02:58,600 --> 00:03:00,100
Please excuse me

47
00:03:04,041 --> 00:03:05,442
Come, sir

48
00:03:06,300 --> 00:03:07,700
Master

49
00:03:08,095 --> 00:03:09,159
Slowly

50
00:03:11,600 --> 00:03:12,821
Let's go

51
00:03:14,200 --> 00:03:15,000
Thank you

52
00:03:24,155 --> 00:03:25,438
Let's go

53
00:03:31,700 --> 00:03:34,400
Why did you bring so many books? Where did you get it from?

54
00:03:34,710 --> 00:03:38,614
I brought those that Wang Ye liked

55
00:03:38,715 --> 00:03:40,778
He asked them to bring it over today

56
00:03:41,149 --> 00:03:43,825
I only need a few books

57
00:03:43,900 --> 00:03:46,000
Why do you want so many from him?

58
00:03:46,971 --> 00:03:48,810
Miss...teach me how to read and write can you?

59
00:03:50,400 --> 00:03:53,000
Did you not want to learn before?

60
00:03:53,352 --> 00:03:55,399
why the change of mind?

61
00:03:56,600 --> 00:03:59,000
Isn't it better for me to know a little reading?

62
00:03:59,923 --> 00:04:01,566
Missy always loves these

63
00:04:01,819 --> 00:04:03,166
so i want to understand it as well

64
00:04:03,395 --> 00:04:05,003
I can keep you company and kill boredom

65
00:04:06,553 --> 00:04:08,251
Missy now has Wang Ye

66
00:04:08,714 --> 00:04:10,476
You're like a pair of celestial lovers

67
00:04:11,300 --> 00:04:13,100
Don't you want my company anymore?

68
00:04:15,400 --> 00:04:16,600
Don't argue with me

69
00:04:17,055 --> 00:04:17,708
Let me ask you

70
00:04:18,500 --> 00:04:20,500
These two past two days

71
00:04:20,593 --> 00:04:22,374
you've heard everything didn't you?

72
00:04:24,969 --> 00:04:26,603
Since you guessed it already

73
00:04:27,111 --> 00:04:28,871
I won't hide it anymore either

74
00:04:31,000 --> 00:04:32,900
Missy and Wang Ye are so knowledgeable

75
00:04:33,500 --> 00:04:35,200
Your conversations flow so smoothly

76
00:04:35,712 --> 00:04:37,264
I don't even know anything

77
00:04:38,200 --> 00:04:42,600
The other day, the both of you were creating poems together

78
00:04:43,684 --> 00:04:46,995
I felt like a block of wood standing there

79
00:04:47,300 --> 00:04:48,700
It was so embarassing

80
00:04:49,902 --> 00:04:52,761
It's great that you're motivated

81
00:04:53,100 --> 00:04:56,600
as long as you want to learn, I am willing to teach you

82
00:04:57,686 --> 00:05:01,395
but as a girl, to know a book, the smarter you become

83
00:05:01,500 --> 00:05:04,400
and this will create more headache in the future

84
00:05:04,600 --> 00:05:08,700
But that's ok

85
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:30,400
Go and ask your little master out

86
00:05:30,400 --> 00:05:31,400
Also Sun Gong Gong

87
00:05:31,500 --> 00:05:35,500
you don't understand him. He doesn't trust anyone

88
00:05:35,600 --> 00:05:38,700
Now it's only her new horse

89
00:05:38,800 --> 00:05:41,000
she refused to come out

90
00:05:41,100 --> 00:05:44,500
If you want to wait here, you will be waiting about two to three hours

91
00:05:44,600 --> 00:05:47,200
then you won't do your big duties

92
00:05:47,200 --> 00:05:48,600
Haiyoo...my dear grandma

93
00:05:48,700 --> 00:05:50,700
She can escape out of it, I can't

94
00:05:50,800 --> 00:05:52,700
I have to serve the Emperor

95
00:05:52,800 --> 00:05:55,400
Sun Gong Gong! I know you're scared of horses

96
00:05:55,400 --> 00:05:58,346
Don't be afraid, the horse is dangerous

97
00:05:58,400 --> 00:06:00,200
but with little master around

98
00:06:00,300 --> 00:06:02,900
it will not hurt you

99
00:06:04,400 --> 00:06:07,600
Your Majesty, why do you fancy such a woman?

100
00:06:09,900 --> 00:06:13,500
Little Master, you're finally out to receive the edict

101
00:06:13,566 --> 00:06:15,036
If you have something to say just say it!

102
00:06:15,400 --> 00:06:17,300
Emporer has an order

103
00:06:21,000 --> 00:06:23,100
Little Master, sorry

104
00:06:23,100 --> 00:06:25,300
You should kneel to recieve the order

105
00:06:29,400 --> 00:06:32,400
By divine edict of the Emperor,

106
00:06:32,400 --> 00:06:34,900
Ms. Ye of Yuanming Garden is intelligent and refined.

107
00:06:35,000 --> 00:06:39,700
She's to be conferred the title of Promise, <br>and taken into the palace to reside. End of edict.

108
00:06:47,800 --> 00:06:51,100
Young Mistress, you have to express your gratitude.

109
00:06:51,600 --> 00:06:53,300
Thanks.

110
00:06:55,000 --> 00:06:57,000
Congratulations, Young Mistress Ye.

111
00:06:57,000 --> 00:06:58,600
You're really fortunate.

112
00:06:58,700 --> 00:07:02,300
All the females in the palace start from being an Official Lady.

113
00:07:02,400 --> 00:07:05,200
Your first step, and you're already a Promise.

114
00:07:05,200 --> 00:07:07,400
If I gave this fortune to you, would you want it?

115
00:07:07,400 --> 00:07:10,200
Young Mistress, you're joking.

116
00:07:10,400 --> 00:07:14,100
You should start packing quickly and get ready to enter the palace.

117
00:07:15,000 --> 00:07:16,700
Where will I be staying in the harem?

118
00:07:16,800 --> 00:07:18,300
The Internal Affairs department will make the arrangements.

119
00:07:18,300 --> 00:07:21,000
What the Internal Affairs Department arranges is their own problem!

120
00:07:21,100 --> 00:07:24,100
Since the Emperor likes me, <br>why is the Internal Affairs Department getting involved?

121
00:07:24,200 --> 00:07:26,500
By nature, I don't like noise and excitement.

122
00:07:26,500 --> 00:07:30,500
Gonggong, please tell His Majesty to arrange a place for me that is quiet and far away from everyone else.

123
00:07:30,600 --> 00:07:31,400
Yes.

124
00:07:31,500 --> 00:07:33,500
His Majesty will definitely make the arrangements.

125
00:07:33,600 --> 00:07:36,000
Young Mistress, please enter the palace quickly.

126
00:07:36,000 --> 00:07:38,500
You still have to express your gratitude to the Emperor.

127
00:07:39,000 --> 00:07:41,400
I won't be able to wait for him to come anymore.

128
00:07:41,400 --> 00:07:43,500
I still promised to perform for him.

129
00:07:43,600 --> 00:07:45,300
Young Mistress, whom are you referring to?

130
00:07:45,304 --> 00:07:47,162
Why do you care who I'm talking about?

131
00:07:55,200 --> 00:07:58,900
Look at this fish. <br>Its eyes are protruding out.

132
00:08:00,200 --> 00:08:02,300
This fish is pretty.

133
00:08:02,600 --> 00:08:07,300
Greetings, Empress Dowager, Empress, and Consort Qi.

134
00:08:07,600 --> 00:08:08,800
Get up.

135
00:08:08,808 --> 00:08:10,384
Thank you, Empress Dowager.

136
00:08:11,800 --> 00:08:14,900
I had no choice but to call you over despite how busy you are.

137
00:08:15,100 --> 00:08:16,700
Your servant doesn't dare.

138
00:08:16,733 --> 00:08:19,369
The matter has been done secretly.

139
00:08:19,369 --> 00:08:22,822
But sooner or later, she'll have to stay in one of the palaces.

140
00:08:23,000 --> 00:08:26,600
How long does His Majesty intend to hide it from me?

141
00:08:28,000 --> 00:08:30,000
I'm asking you.

142
00:08:30,100 --> 00:08:32,000
Has the new girl entered the palace yet?

143
00:08:32,200 --> 00:08:35,500
What new girl? <br>How did I not know of it?

144
00:08:35,500 --> 00:08:38,800
His Majesty finds you magnanimous and of good character.

145
00:08:38,900 --> 00:08:41,400
Always approving, never rejecting.

146
00:08:41,500 --> 00:08:44,400
So he dares to pull all kinds of people into the palace.

147
00:08:44,800 --> 00:08:46,700
Empress Dowager, don't be angry.

148
00:08:46,707 --> 00:08:49,924
It's just her status that is a little low.

149
00:08:50,000 --> 00:08:54,500
It's a bit similar to Lady Miaoyin in the past. <br>That's all.

150
00:08:55,000 --> 00:08:58,300
At most, it'll be like the previous Eight Prince's mother.

151
00:08:58,400 --> 00:09:01,100
Only a lowly slave.

152
00:09:01,200 --> 00:09:05,000
That lowly slave was at least a servant official

153
00:09:05,600 --> 00:09:07,500
The one His Majesty has picked this time...

154
00:09:07,600 --> 00:09:10,100
is a horse trainer from Yuanming Garden...

155
00:09:10,100 --> 00:09:14,200
who performs shows.

156
00:09:14,600 --> 00:09:16,700
Empress Dowager,

157
00:09:16,800 --> 00:09:19,400
she has already entered the palace.

158
00:09:19,500 --> 00:09:21,500
Because she was at Yuan Ming Yuan and couldn't enter the palace

159
00:09:21,500 --> 00:09:24,200
The emperor was worrying day and night

160
00:09:24,300 --> 00:09:27,300
He titled her as Promise, and had her brought into the palace.

161
00:09:27,400 --> 00:09:28,600
Has it been decided where she will be staying?

162
00:09:28,661 --> 00:09:29,939
Not yet.

163
00:09:30,000 --> 00:09:32,100
But Promise Ye said...

164
00:09:32,104 --> 00:09:35,753
that she wants to stay somewhere quiet with few people.

165
00:09:35,817 --> 00:09:37,331
Hear that, all of you.

166
00:09:37,350 --> 00:09:40,775
She's just entered the palace,<br>and she's already making demands.

167
00:09:41,000 --> 00:09:42,400
Exactly.

168
00:09:42,800 --> 00:09:44,600
Has His Majesty mentioned where is to be given to her?

169
00:09:44,700 --> 00:09:48,000
We have to wait 2 days before they clean up the room

170
00:09:48,000 --> 00:09:50,900
His Majesty said for her to stay at <br>Yang Xin Hall's side wing for the time being.

171
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:52,700
How can that be allowed?

172
00:09:54,200 --> 00:09:56,300
Tell the Emperor...

173
00:09:56,342 --> 00:09:59,564
Chun Xi Hall in Shou Kang Palace is empty

174
00:09:59,600 --> 00:10:01,400
Get someone to clean it up immediately for her.

175
00:10:01,400 --> 00:10:02,200
Yes

176
00:10:02,276 --> 00:10:04,001
Chunxi Hall is to be given to her?

177
00:10:04,100 --> 00:10:06,300
Isn't that too much of an honor for her?

178
00:10:06,317 --> 00:10:07,819
Naturally not.

179
00:10:07,834 --> 00:10:10,068
In a situation like this,

180
00:10:10,100 --> 00:10:13,100
I'm afraid that she will be promoted again

181
00:10:13,600 --> 00:10:15,700
She likes the quiet.

182
00:10:15,700 --> 00:10:18,600
There are no place more quiet than Shou Kang Palace

183
00:10:18,700 --> 00:10:21,700
Let her live right under my watch,

184
00:10:21,700 --> 00:10:24,300
and she won't be able to play any tricks.

185
00:10:42,600 --> 00:10:45,000
Dispense with ceremony. Sit.

186
00:10:51,800 --> 00:10:53,100
Why?

187
00:10:53,144 --> 00:10:54,796
You're not happy?

188
00:10:55,000 --> 00:10:57,600
Are you not used to living here?

189
00:10:57,600 --> 00:10:59,700
It's the same everywhere.

190
00:11:00,400 --> 00:11:02,300
You've been here for a few days now.

191
00:11:02,300 --> 00:11:04,300
I haven't seen you smile once.

192
00:11:05,300 --> 00:11:07,200
If you feel that the palace is constrained,

193
00:11:07,300 --> 00:11:10,000
I'll take you to Yuanming Garden for a few days when I'm free.

194
00:11:10,100 --> 00:11:12,000
Your Majesty is busy with Court.

195
00:11:12,000 --> 00:11:14,300
You don't have to worry about me.

196
00:11:14,600 --> 00:11:16,900
Furthermore, not smiling...

197
00:11:17,000 --> 00:11:19,900
is because by nature, I do not like to smile.

198
00:11:21,200 --> 00:11:23,700
No other reason.

199
00:11:27,400 --> 00:11:31,000
Actually, when you don't smile, you're even prettier.

200
00:11:32,500 --> 00:11:37,200
Niangniang, <br>how did His Majesty title such a lowly lass as a Promise?

201
00:11:38,400 --> 00:11:40,400
Empress...

202
00:11:40,400 --> 00:11:42,200
The ancestral rules state that when a courtier is titled,

203
00:11:42,300 --> 00:11:44,100
they have to start from a lady official

204
00:11:44,100 --> 00:11:49,100
Ye Lanyi is not a courtier. Moreover, the Emperor likes her. <br>What's impossible?

205
00:11:49,100 --> 00:11:51,800
She was titled in the afternoon, had dinner with the Emperor

206
00:11:51,900 --> 00:11:54,200
And at night she was sent into Yangxin Hall<br> to attend to consummate the union.

207
00:11:54,200 --> 00:11:57,000
For these few days, His Majesty has only had relations with her!

208
00:11:57,000 --> 00:11:59,300
I have never seen His Majesty like that before.

209
00:11:59,400 --> 00:12:01,900
You've never seen it? <br>I've never seen it too!

210
00:12:02,000 --> 00:12:04,300
This is what deviousness and cunning means

211
00:12:04,400 --> 00:12:06,600
Today, when I went to Yangxin Hall to pay my respects,

212
00:12:06,600 --> 00:12:09,000
I saw Promise Ye's appearance.

213
00:12:09,000 --> 00:12:11,100
Her aura so uncouth.

214
00:12:11,200 --> 00:12:13,800
What on earth does His Majesty like about her?

215
00:12:13,800 --> 00:12:16,100
If Concubine Qi has the ability,

216
00:12:16,200 --> 00:12:18,500
why doesn't she display that aura too?

217
00:12:18,600 --> 00:12:20,700
His Majesty will like it too.

218
00:12:22,386 --> 00:12:24,112
For Ms. Ye to receive this much favor...

219
00:12:24,139 --> 00:12:25,637
is worrying indeed.

220
00:12:26,500 --> 00:12:28,100
If she were to spawn some lowly creature someday,

221
00:12:28,200 --> 00:12:29,400
who knows what would happen?

222
00:12:30,100 --> 00:12:31,300
If Heaven were protecting us,

223
00:12:31,400 --> 00:12:33,100
may she never give birth.

224
00:12:47,252 --> 00:13:02,460
<br>

225
00:13:20,900 --> 00:13:22,000
Promise Ye.

226
00:13:24,700 --> 00:13:25,800
Seventeenth Prince?

227
00:13:28,000 --> 00:13:29,000
You're here?

228
00:13:29,400 --> 00:13:30,500
I haven't seen you for some time,

229
00:13:30,600 --> 00:13:32,000
and you're now a Promise.

230
00:13:36,200 --> 00:13:37,700
No one ask if I was willing to or not.

231
00:13:38,800 --> 00:13:40,300
And here I am in the palace.

232
00:13:40,600 --> 00:13:41,800
And I'm a Promise.

233
00:13:44,000 --> 00:13:45,500
I heard about what happened to you.

234
00:13:46,400 --> 00:13:47,900
You seem depressed

235
00:13:48,900 --> 00:13:50,600
Everything here is so dirty.

236
00:13:52,000 --> 00:13:53,900
My Hundred Horse Garden is still the cleanest

237
00:13:58,800 --> 00:14:00,200
Do you still remember that year?

238
00:14:00,600 --> 00:14:01,900
You had a high fever.

239
00:14:02,631 --> 00:14:03,684
I remember.

240
00:14:04,900 --> 00:14:06,300
That was seven years ago...

241
00:14:06,700 --> 00:14:08,000
I was ill and almost dying.

242
00:14:08,500 --> 00:14:10,300
No one would care about a lowly slave like me.

243
00:14:11,200 --> 00:14:12,900
It was you who saw me by chance,

244
00:14:13,500 --> 00:14:14,800
and had the Imperial Physician save me.

245
00:14:15,000 --> 00:14:16,200
When I first saved you then,

246
00:14:16,600 --> 00:14:17,700
it wasn't to see you...

247
00:14:17,713 --> 00:14:18,958
so filled with despair today.

248
00:14:19,459 --> 00:14:20,791
But what else can I do?

249
00:14:21,800 --> 00:14:23,200
I can't go where I want to.

250
00:14:24,303 --> 00:14:25,806
And where I'm staying...

251
00:14:26,100 --> 00:14:27,200
makes me feel disgusted.

252
00:14:27,700 --> 00:14:29,000
and fills me with utter hopelessness.

253
00:14:30,700 --> 00:14:31,800
You have to take care of yourself

254
00:14:32,700 --> 00:14:34,500
My memory of Ye Lanyi...

255
00:14:34,500 --> 00:14:36,500
has a beautiful smile, and a strong character.

256
00:14:36,500 --> 00:14:40,700
No matter bitter it is, <br>she'll find a way to find the sweetness in it and be happy.

257
00:14:44,500 --> 00:14:46,500
I have never been able to repay...

258
00:14:46,500 --> 00:14:48,800
you for your kindness many years ago, my lord.

259
00:14:49,673 --> 00:14:51,862
Since you want me to live well,

260
00:14:52,036 --> 00:14:54,103
I will definitely listen to you.

261
00:14:55,500 --> 00:14:56,800
That's great.

262
00:15:00,400 --> 00:15:01,600
Huan Er.

263
00:15:03,900 --> 00:15:05,700
Why did you come so suddenly?

264
00:15:05,800 --> 00:15:08,800
When I was done with my errands, <br>I rushed over to meet you.

265
00:15:09,400 --> 00:15:12,500
Before..didn't I say that my heart was unease?

266
00:15:12,900 --> 00:15:15,500
I've thought of something that will allow both our hearts to be at ease.

267
00:15:24,900 --> 00:15:26,500
A marriage notice?

268
00:15:26,500 --> 00:15:28,700
Yes, a marriage notice.

