306
00:19:37,400 --> 00:19:39,300
Although Imperial Brother wishes to give me this task

307
00:19:39,700 --> 00:19:41,600
But I am not talented

308
00:19:42,800 --> 00:19:44,400
I want to use you

309
00:19:45,600 --> 00:19:48,900
Precisely because you don't have many ties in Court

310
00:19:49,700 --> 00:19:54,500
If you go in plain clothes, most people won't recognise you

311
00:19:54,500 --> 00:19:56,500
Now the stretch along Yunnan

312
00:19:56,900 --> 00:19:59,100
