317
00:20:12,400 --> 00:20:14,500
Imperial Consort Shu is from Yunnan

318
00:20:14,800 --> 00:20:18,900
For you to make a trip to Yunnan is more appropriate

319
00:20:21,600 --> 00:20:25,800
Although your brother is untalented, since Your Majesty has asked, I cannot decline

320
00:20:26,900 --> 00:20:29,200
I will do my best

321
00:20:30,000 --> 00:20:31,500
Good

322
00:20:31,500 --> 00:20:35,100
Go and get ready, leave and return early

323
00:20:37,900 --> 00:20:39,800
Your brother takes his leave

324
00:20:46,200 --> 00:20:47,700
Su Pei Sheng

325
00:20:51,100 --> 00:20:52,200
Your Majesty

326
00:20:53,200 --> 00:20:55,300
Call for Minister Zhang Ting Yu

327
00:20:55,300 --> 00:20:56,500
Yes

328
00:21:06,100 --> 00:21:08,800
Your Official pays his respects to you

329
00:21:11,600 --> 00:21:13,100
Get up.

330
00:21:18,300 --> 00:21:19,800
I summoned you here today...

331
00:21:20,200 --> 00:21:23,300
because of the matter regarding Prince Guo advancing to Yunnan.

332
00:21:23,900 --> 00:21:27,900
You must send some trustworthy people to protect him in secret.

333
00:21:28,800 --> 00:21:30,100
At the same time,

334
00:21:30,100 --> 00:21:34,100
prevent him from getting too involved in politics.

335
00:21:34,600 --> 00:21:36,600
Every time he reaches a location,

336
00:21:36,600 --> 00:21:39,200
whom he speaks to, what he does...

337
00:21:39,900 --> 00:21:43,000
investigate it closely and report it back promptly.

338
00:21:44,100 --> 00:21:45,300
Yes.

339
00:21:56,700 --> 00:21:58,153
Physician Wen.

340
00:21:58,153 --> 00:22:00,000
Is the medicine ready?

341
00:22:02,700 --> 00:22:04,100
Yes.

342
00:22:10,700 --> 00:22:12,400
Be careful when you use it.

343
00:22:14,900 --> 00:22:16,300
Many thanks.

344
00:22:16,800 --> 00:22:18,100
Don't thank me.

345
00:22:19,200 --> 00:22:21,800
I'm just afraid for Huan Er's wellbeing.

346
00:22:23,900 --> 00:22:25,400
Still, many thanks.

347
00:22:37,900 --> 00:22:40,000
Why were you so careless when you dismounted your horse?

348
00:22:40,000 --> 00:22:42,700
Such a good cloak, needlessly ripped

349
00:22:42,700 --> 00:22:44,800
I thought about the fact that I hadn't seen you for four days already.

350
00:22:44,800 --> 00:22:46,500
So I hurried when I got off the horse.

351
00:22:47,000 --> 00:22:49,400
It's just a clothing. It isn't worth much.

352
00:22:50,000 --> 00:22:53,300
The mountain roads are slippery in the snow and it's easy for the horse to slip

353
00:22:53,700 --> 00:22:55,900
What's the point of you rushing over here?

354
00:22:56,600 --> 00:23:00,500
This time you cut your clothing, what if the next time you hurt yourself?

355
00:23:00,500 --> 00:23:02,400
Are you intentionally out to make me worry?

356
00:23:02,400 --> 00:23:04,200
I'll just promise you then.

357
00:23:04,700 --> 00:23:06,500
I don't want to hurt myself either.

358
00:23:06,800 --> 00:23:09,200
If I'm hurt, how will I come to see you?

359
00:23:10,300 --> 00:23:12,000
What a slippery tongue.

360
00:23:15,000 --> 00:23:18,800
