361
00:23:19,800 --> 00:23:22,300
I'll just leave you to wear a torn clothing all over.

362
00:23:26,000 --> 00:23:27,900
You're leaving tomorrow?

363
00:23:27,900 --> 00:23:30,400
23rd of the 12th month. In about a month.

364
00:23:30,600 --> 00:23:33,700
