366
00:23:35,100 --> 00:23:37,500
I will definitely be back within 40 days.

367
00:23:39,000 --> 00:23:40,300
40 days.

368
00:23:41,300 --> 00:23:43,000
Another full cycle of the moon.

369
00:23:43,000 --> 00:23:44,900
40 days are very short!

370
00:23:45,200 --> 00:23:46,789
I've already made all the arrangements.

371
00:23:46,800 --> 00:23:48,100
When I come back this time,

372
00:23:48,163 --> 00:23:49,692
I will take you to leave this place.

373
00:23:49,700 --> 00:23:51,000
Really?

374
00:23:56,600 --> 00:23:58,600
This is...?

375
00:24:04,471 --> 00:24:06,110
It seems like fragrance powder.

376
00:24:06,200 --> 00:24:07,254
It's a medicine from Physician Wen

377
00:24:07,254 --> 00:24:08,800
to fake death

378
00:24:09,500 --> 00:24:11,300
It's called the "7-day Unconscious Powder"

379
00:24:11,300 --> 00:24:13,100
Made from Datura flowers

380
00:24:13,100 --> 00:24:16,500
After taking it, it'll be like you've stopped breathing

381
00:24:16,800 --> 00:24:18,700
Exactly like a dead person

382
00:24:18,700 --> 00:24:22,100
7 days later you'll be able to wake up

383
00:24:23,700 --> 00:24:25,500
In the end, he's still willing to help me

384
00:24:26,600 --> 00:24:29,500
Physician Wen has indeed put in a lot of effort for us

385
00:24:29,667 --> 00:24:31,378
We should really thank him

386
00:24:33,600 --> 00:24:35,300
I've made the preparations

387
00:24:35,300 --> 00:24:37,200
Once everything is in place

388
00:24:37,200 --> 00:24:38,700
Huan Er.

389
00:24:39,200 --> 00:24:42,500
When that time comes, <br>we'll be together forever.

390
00:24:43,200 --> 00:24:45,900
I'll wait for you to come back, and wait for everything to be resolved

391
00:24:45,900 --> 00:24:47,900
Only then can I rest easy

392
00:24:48,700 --> 00:24:51,300
Huan'er. This is a matter of governance

393
00:24:51,600 --> 00:24:53,000
I can't not go.

394
00:24:53,900 --> 00:24:55,400
It's just 40 days.

395
00:24:55,600 --> 00:24:57,200
I will definitely wait for you.

