00:25:00,800 --> 00:25:03,800
In the past, my aunt from Jiangnan

397
00:25:04,200 --> 00:25:08,000
There's a bridge on the west lake in Hangzhou called the "Long Bridge"

398
00:25:08,900 --> 00:25:10,200
Long Bridge?

399
00:25:11,700 --> 00:25:13,100
Is the bridge very long?

400
00:25:13,600 --> 00:25:15,400
Actually the bridge isn't very long

401
00:25:15,400 --> 00:25:17,100
It's called the Long Bridge

402
00:25:17,129 --> 00:25:19,381
because the locals always say

403
00:25:19,400 --> 00:25:22,900
that Liang Shan Bo bo Zhu Ying Tai (famous historical lovers) said their goodbyes there

404
00:25:22,900 --> 00:25:24,500
Unwilling to let go of each other

405
00:25:24,800 --> 00:25:28,300
So the short bridge seemed like a really long one

406
00:25:29,500 --> 00:25:31,200
The pain of separation

407
00:25:31,200 --> 00:25:34,000
has been the same since the ancient times

408
00:25:34,000 --> 00:25:36,700
I don't want us to be Liang Shan Bo and Zhu Ying Tai

409
00:25:36,700 --> 00:25:39,400
She married crying and he died young throwing up blood

410
00:25:39,450 --> 00:25:41,317
In the end they could only leave the Earth as butterflies

411
00:25:41,800 --> 00:25:43,800
We're much luckier than they were

412
00:25:46,300 --> 00:25:49,100
What was I thinking? Making an analogy out of them...

413
00:25:51,682 --> 00:25:53,372
I'm thinking too much today

414
00:25:53,400 --> 00:25:55,300
So I can't really stomach any inauspicious words

415
00:25:56,600 --> 00:25:58,600
It seems like a man's heart

416
00:25:59,100 --> 00:26:01,200
that is in the hand's of his love

417
00:26:02,000 --> 00:26:03,900
can no longer be free and easy

418
00:26:05,700 --> 00:26:07,100
Go and be free and easy

419
00:26:07,100 --> 00:26:09,200
Prince Guo is suave

420
00:26:09,452 --> 00:26:12,665
Is he afraid that no other beautiful ladies would pine after him?

421
00:26:17,500 --> 00:26:21,000
You, really! Bullying me this way

422
00:26:21,000 --> 00:26:22,900
You're trying to make me angry

423
00:26:22,900 --> 00:26:24,700
Who asked you to speak nonsense?

424
00:26:28,700 --> 00:26:30,900
Although the flowers are blooming

425
00:26:30,923 --> 00:26:33,030
But please hurry back

426
00:26:33,100 --> 00:26:36,100
because I will wait for you here

427
00:26:37,100 --> 00:26:38,600
With you here

428
00:26:39,300 --> 00:26:41,200
I will return home as expediently as possible

429
00:26:52,000 --> 00:27:05,700
<br>

430
00:27:24,200 --> 00:27:25,600
Huan'er!

431
00:27:29,700 --> 00:27:31,700
Huan'er!

432
00:27:46,200 --> 00:27:47,700
Huan'er

433
00:27:58,500 --> 00:28:00,300
I will return very quickly

434
00:28:00,300 --> 00:28:01,900
I wait for your return

435
00:28:07,900 --> 00:28:09,500
Wait for me

436
00:28:24,300 --> 00:28:26,700
I wait for your return!

437
00:28:43,600 --> 00:28:45,500
I wait for your return

438
00:29:08,600 --> 00:29:10,100
My lady.

439
00:29:10,100 --> 00:29:13,200
I've sent the blankets to Anxi Hall as you've instructed

440
00:29:13,200 --> 00:29:15,500
Imperial Consort sends along her regards

441
00:29:15,500 --> 00:29:17,900
and said that Wang'ye will be home soon

442
00:29:17,900 --> 00:29:20,700
At that time, the both of you should go together to pay your respects

443
00:29:21,200 --> 00:29:24,400
These two days I've been feeling lazy and sleepy

444
00:29:25,000 --> 00:29:27,500
But Yun Li will be back within 10 days

445
00:29:27,900 --> 00:29:30,100
I can always go with him then

446
00:29:32,400 --> 00:29:35,900
Priestess Mochou, an esteemed guest from the palace has come.

447
00:29:38,800 --> 00:29:40,200
Jiejie!

448
00:29:40,200 --> 00:29:41,500
Huan Er!

449
00:29:42,200 --> 00:29:45,400
It's all my fault!<br>I waited till today to come see you.

450
00:29:45,400 --> 00:29:46,500
Sit.

451
00:29:51,300 --> 00:29:55,500
This is our first time seeing each other in a few years, why are we crying?

452
00:29:59,800 --> 00:30:04,000
Out of the blue, how could you let my sister stay in such a secluded place?

453
00:30:04,600 --> 00:30:09,200
When I came over from Ganlu Temple, <br>even on a sedan, it took a whole hour!

454
00:30:09,500 --> 00:30:12,700
Is this how Ganlu Temple looks after women from the palace who come here to pray?

455
00:30:14,300 --> 00:30:16,200
I've been sick recently

456
00:30:16,200 --> 00:30:18,100
That's why I moved here to recuperate

457
00:30:18,100 --> 00:30:19,800
It's not the abbess' fault

458
00:30:19,846 --> 00:30:21,707
Mochou is kind

459
00:30:22,000 --> 00:30:23,500
Yes, yes.

460
00:30:23,500 --> 00:30:26,400
Mochou was sick, that's why she was moved here

461
00:30:28,086 --> 00:30:29,816
All of you go out and wait

462
00:30:29,816 --> 00:30:32,133
I have private words to speak to Mochou

463
00:30:33,000 --> 00:30:34,100
Yes.

464
00:30:34,100 --> 00:30:35,587
Other people aside,

465
00:30:35,600 --> 00:30:38,100
Priestess Jing Bai is hale and healthy

466
00:30:38,100 --> 00:30:41,200
Go and sweep the snow off the path towards the palace

467
00:30:41,900 --> 00:30:45,500
In order to show your sincerity to my lady, please complete this task alone

468
00:30:47,400 --> 00:30:48,400
Yes.

469
00:30:53,000 --> 00:30:55,100
Why are you making things difficult for her like that?

470
00:30:55,800 --> 00:30:58,400
You've been thoroughly humiliated at Ganlu Temple!

471
00:31:00,700 --> 00:31:01,800
Not at all.

472
00:31:01,800 --> 00:31:03,400
You're still trying to hide it from me?

473
00:31:03,400 --> 00:31:05,300
Do you think I really don't know?

474
00:31:05,700 --> 00:31:08,400
You were dismissed from the palace under disgraceful circumstances

475
00:31:08,900 --> 00:31:11,900
Which person on this earth doesn't look down on the disgraced?

476
00:31:12,300 --> 00:31:14,800
Even if one is a nun, they may not be able to look past it

477
00:31:16,000 --> 00:31:18,100
When I wanted to come see you

478
00:31:18,100 --> 00:31:20,300
that Jing Bai continuously tried to rebuff me

479
00:31:20,300 --> 00:31:22,800
First she said the weather was cold. <br>Then she said the road was slippery.

480
00:31:22,800 --> 00:31:26,400
I just said a few sentences to you, <br>and she already looked so guilty!

481
00:31:26,400 --> 00:31:28,800
Obviously, she has been bullying you all these days.

482
00:31:29,456 --> 00:31:31,532
I punished her in front of you.

483
00:31:31,600 --> 00:31:33,700
On one hand, it is to punish her

484
00:31:33,700 --> 00:31:38,200
On the other hand, it is to show that you weren't the one that put me up to punishing her

485
00:31:38,600 --> 00:31:40,300
You're so thoughtful.

486
00:31:40,900 --> 00:31:42,300
It's fine. It's fine.

487
00:31:42,300 --> 00:31:44,800
I just think that you're suffering so much here

488
00:31:44,800 --> 00:31:48,500
And the Priestess said that you were heavily sick and moved out of Gan Lu Temple

489
00:31:48,557 --> 00:31:51,436
During the journey over here, I was so worried!

490
00:31:51,900 --> 00:31:55,000
Now that I see that you're well and healthy

491
00:31:55,000 --> 00:31:57,300
I can be rest assured too.

492
00:32:00,000 --> 00:32:01,615
I heard that you got promoted to be a Concubine.

493
00:32:01,615 --> 00:32:03,600
I was so happy for many days!

494
00:32:04,400 --> 00:32:06,300
What's the use of being a Concubine?

495
00:32:06,300 --> 00:32:08,400
That doesn't matter to me

496
00:32:10,200 --> 00:32:11,900
Why do you do that to yourself?

497
00:32:13,100 --> 00:32:16,400
For these two years, it seems like His Majesty is punishing himself.

498
00:32:16,600 --> 00:32:18,700
He only buries his head in Court affairs.

499
00:32:19,000 --> 00:32:20,600
After you left,

500
00:32:20,600 --> 00:32:23,300
His Majesty's attitude toward the harem has cooled a lot too.

501
00:32:24,200 --> 00:32:26,000
Although there is also Concubine Qi,

502
00:32:26,000 --> 00:32:29,100
and a Lingering Kang and Concubine Zhen

503
00:32:29,700 --> 00:32:32,700
But it's hard for one to say that he really likes any one

504
00:32:33,300 --> 00:32:36,900
Until just recently, Promise Ye entered the palace and things got a little bit better

505
00:32:37,700 --> 00:32:40,300
Now His Majesty treats me courteously

506
00:32:40,703 --> 00:32:44,017
That's good too. <br>Now with the status of a Concubine,

507
00:32:44,100 --> 00:32:47,300
it's easier to do some things too.

508
00:32:47,300 --> 00:32:50,000
Fangruo Gugu being able to visit me frequently...

509
00:32:50,000 --> 00:32:52,300
it's thanks to you asking Empress Dowager for permission?

510
00:32:52,900 --> 00:32:54,500
You're doing so much for me.

511
00:32:54,500 --> 00:32:56,200
If the situation were reversed, and I were the one suffering,

512
00:32:56,200 --> 00:32:58,200
you would do the same for me.

513
00:32:59,400 --> 00:33:01,900
Huan Er, I listened to you.

514
00:33:01,900 --> 00:33:05,800
I kept my head down and out of the Empress' notice

515
00:33:06,300 --> 00:33:08,400
I just spent my time dutifully serving the Empress Dowager

516
00:33:08,400 --> 00:33:10,500
And helped Consort Jing look after Long Yue

517
00:33:11,400 --> 00:33:16,000
Just so that the day will come when I can clear your name

518
00:33:16,800 --> 00:33:20,600
But after so many years, I haven't been able to get anything useful

519
00:33:24,489 --> 00:33:27,059
It's not easy to leave the palace, especially not at this time of the year

520
00:33:27,447 --> 00:33:29,175
How were you able to come out?

521
00:33:30,500 --> 00:33:32,800
A few days ago, Princess Wenyi fell sick.

522
00:33:32,800 --> 00:33:34,700
Although the physician saw her,

523
00:33:34,753 --> 00:33:38,071
But the priestess at Bao Hua Temple said that there's a spiritual disturbance

524
00:33:38,100 --> 00:33:41,600
So all the tablets of executed court ladies have to be moved to Gan Lu Temple

525
00:33:42,200 --> 00:33:45,600
But to do this in the Zheng month (12th month) is inauspicious

526
00:33:45,600 --> 00:33:47,800
Why was it handed to you?

527
00:33:47,800 --> 00:33:49,100
The Priest said

528
00:33:49,100 --> 00:33:54,000
