00:33:54,500 --> 00:33:57,600
Of course, I'm not the only woman who fits that criteria.

530
00:33:57,600 --> 00:34:00,200
But the others found it taboo.

531
00:34:00,200 --> 00:34:02,400
That's why I had the chance.

532
00:34:02,676 --> 00:34:05,063
You've always been circumspect about such matters

533
00:34:05,443 --> 00:34:09,116
and would never get involved with these sort of spiritual things

534
00:34:09,877 --> 00:34:11,382
Sister Mei

535
00:34:11,676 --> 00:34:14,239
Are you sure that you're only here to see me

536
00:34:14,400 --> 00:34:16,600
as a convenient aside from that task?

537
00:34:19,900 --> 00:34:22,600
Since you've discovered it, I won't keep it from you.

538
00:34:23,500 --> 00:34:26,800
I had Physician Wen give Princess Wenyi some medicine to increase her temperature.

539
00:34:27,127 --> 00:34:30,862
And then bribed the Priest from Bao Hua Temple to mention the cleansing of the spirits

540
00:34:30,900 --> 00:34:33,700
That's how I got the opportunity to meet you.

541
00:34:33,700 --> 00:34:35,400
You put in so much effort...

542
00:34:35,400 --> 00:34:37,700
Something severe must have happened?

543
00:34:37,900 --> 00:34:39,400
Has something happened to Longyue?

544
00:34:39,400 --> 00:34:41,600
No, no. Not Longyue.

545
00:34:41,800 --> 00:34:44,300
She's fine. Nothing's wrong with her at all.

546
00:34:45,400 --> 00:34:46,500
It's...

547
00:34:47,700 --> 00:34:52,400
Your father. He's fallen gravely ill in Ninggu Tower

548
00:34:56,500 --> 00:34:58,400
Father was fine.

549
00:34:59,100 --> 00:35:00,900
How could he be ill to the extent that it's life-threatening?

550
00:35:00,900 --> 00:35:04,900
Yes. Although Uncle was exiled, his body has always been healthy.

551
00:35:05,500 --> 00:35:08,600
I was hesitant for many days regarding telling you about it.

552
00:35:09,300 --> 00:35:12,600
I was afraid that if you found out, <br>you'd just be upset over it.

553
00:35:13,100 --> 00:35:16,100
But... after thinking it through,

554
00:35:16,100 --> 00:35:20,700
I'm worried about Uncle's safety, <br>and could stop myself from telling you about it.

555
00:35:20,700 --> 00:35:22,400
Father has always been healthy.

556
00:35:23,500 --> 00:35:25,200
What on earth happened?

557
00:35:25,700 --> 00:35:27,400
That's exactly where the problem lies.

558
00:35:27,400 --> 00:35:29,500
If it is heaven's will then it is alright

559
00:35:30,000 --> 00:35:31,700
If it is a human's will

560
00:35:31,703 --> 00:35:34,040
then it's really frightening

561
00:35:34,040 --> 00:35:35,969
Jie Jie thinks

562
00:35:35,969 --> 00:35:38,136
that some one was deliberately out to harm him?

563
00:35:38,136 --> 00:35:41,682
I'm afraid that it may be from the Empress' camp.

564
00:35:41,682 --> 00:35:45,247
Otherwise it's people from the Gua'er'jia clan

565
00:35:45,300 --> 00:35:47,700
To think that even after so long,

566
00:35:47,703 --> 00:35:50,107
that they'll keep persisting without letting go

567
00:35:50,344 --> 00:35:52,712
Then Zhen clan has been imprisoned in Ni Gu Tower

568
00:35:52,800 --> 00:35:54,900
I've even left the temple to come here

569
00:35:54,900 --> 00:35:57,500
Why won't they let us off?

570
00:35:57,500 --> 00:36:00,800
Huan Er, now is not the time to be sad.

571
00:36:00,800 --> 00:36:02,800
Uncle was targeted

572
00:36:02,900 --> 00:36:06,600
Who knows whether the next target will be you?

573
00:36:06,600 --> 00:36:10,600
You have to think of a way to get Uncle sent back to the capital to be treated.

574
00:36:10,600 --> 00:36:13,500
With careful treatment, he may still be able to recover.

575
00:36:14,100 --> 00:36:15,600
What you said is right.

576
00:36:16,111 --> 00:36:17,624
At this point in time,

577
00:36:18,000 --> 00:36:20,200
The most important are those who are alive.

578
00:36:21,173 --> 00:36:23,109
Regarding Father's treatment,

579
00:36:23,491 --> 00:36:25,158
I will do my best to think of a way.

580
00:36:25,200 --> 00:36:26,500
Yes.

581
00:36:28,900 --> 00:36:32,900
Niangniang, the time is up. <br>We must return to the palace before it gets dark.

582
00:36:32,900 --> 00:36:36,200
Alright. I understand. Have the sedan waiting.

583
00:36:36,200 --> 00:36:38,700
Yes, Niang'niang shouldn't miss the auspicious hour

584
00:36:38,700 --> 00:36:40,400
Huan Er.

585
00:36:41,100 --> 00:36:42,700
I'm leaving now.

586
00:36:43,200 --> 00:36:45,000
Just remember one thing.

587
00:36:45,400 --> 00:36:47,200
Take good care of yourself.

588
00:36:47,200 --> 00:36:49,400
That's the most important thing, alright?

589
00:36:52,200 --> 00:36:53,800
The palace is dangerous.

590
00:36:54,800 --> 00:36:56,800
You have to be careful too.

591
00:36:57,700 --> 00:36:59,400
When we'll meet again...

592
00:37:00,400 --> 00:37:02,900
is anyone's guess.

593
00:37:04,400 --> 00:37:06,200
As long as we're both safe and sound,

594
00:37:06,200 --> 00:37:09,700
why does it matter whether or not we meet?

595
00:37:19,100 --> 00:37:20,800
You must take care.

596
00:37:22,900 --> 00:37:24,500
You as well.

597
00:37:31,500 --> 00:37:44,788
<br>

598
00:37:56,800 --> 00:37:59,300
Why hasn't mistress eaten dinner again?

599
00:38:00,100 --> 00:38:03,400
Something happened to His Lordship. I'm very upset too.

600
00:38:05,800 --> 00:38:08,100
I just hope His Lordship can return as soon as possible

601
00:38:08,100 --> 00:38:10,100
So that he can help

602
00:38:14,800 --> 00:38:16,800
Mistress, what's wrong?

603
00:38:16,800 --> 00:38:18,700
Did you eat something bad?

604
00:38:24,100 --> 00:38:25,900
Could it be...?

605
00:38:27,400 --> 00:38:29,200
Congratulations, Mistress.

606
00:38:30,000 --> 00:38:32,700
It's not even been a month. Lower your volume.

607
00:38:33,900 --> 00:38:37,000
Mistress, you should tell Grand Concubine. It'll make her happy.

608
00:38:37,400 --> 00:38:39,500
Something just happened to my father.

609
00:38:39,500 --> 00:38:41,400
I can't bring myself to be happy.

610
00:38:43,100 --> 00:38:44,800
I'll wait for Yunli to return.

611
00:38:45,000 --> 00:38:46,800
We'll tell Grand Concubine together then.

612
00:38:52,700 --> 00:38:54,100
Huanbi.

613
00:38:59,000 --> 00:39:01,900
The one in my womb is your little nephew.

614
00:39:04,000 --> 00:39:07,100
Yurao and our parents are in Ning Gu Tower

615
00:39:08,300 --> 00:39:11,800
I'm afraid for the rest of our lives, we can only rely on each other as sisters

616
00:39:13,300 --> 00:39:15,500
My child is also your child

617
00:39:16,400 --> 00:39:19,700
From now on we'll raise him together

618
00:39:20,026 --> 00:39:21,389
Is that okay?

619
00:39:22,400 --> 00:39:23,700
Is that really true?

620
00:39:28,700 --> 00:39:30,700
Elder Sister and His Lordship's child

621
00:39:31,700 --> 00:39:33,700
is also my child

622
00:39:35,900 --> 00:39:39,100
Some things have already been decided, and can't be changed.

623
00:39:40,000 --> 00:39:42,800
If there are changes, it would only hurt people

624
00:39:43,900 --> 00:39:47,700
What I can give to you, I'll give it all to you.

625
00:39:50,100 --> 00:39:51,500
I understand

626
00:39:52,100 --> 00:39:55,500
Somethings that are not destined to be mine...

627
00:39:56,600 --> 00:39:58,700
can't be forced.

										

 
 


   
 

  
   
 
 


 

										